      "title": "PUCSL to probe power cut on 5th Lane last night",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The PUCSL said today an investigation will be launched over the power outage around 5th Lane, where the private residence of Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe is located, at the time it was attacked last night.",
        "PUCSL said there was no scheduled power cuts at that time and they will probe as to how the power was out at that time."
